<paragraph blockId="4.[151,1437,932,1282]" pageId="4" pageNumber="235">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,280,932,958]" pageId="4" pageNumber="235">Type data:</emphasis>
<materialsCitation ID-GBIF-Occurrence="3014903376" collectionCode="ZMB" country="Haiti" location="Haiti" pageId="4" pageNumber="235" specimenCount="1">
This species was described based on a single female specimen collected by the German merchant and botanist Carl August Ehrenberg (1801‒1849). Carl dedicated himself to commerce and travelled through Saint Thomas (1827‒1828), 
<collectingCountry box="[407,463,1004,1030]" name="Haiti" pageId="4" pageNumber="235">Haiti</collectingCountry>
(1828‒1831) and 
<collectingCountry box="[670,756,1004,1030]" name="Mexico" pageId="4" pageNumber="235">Mexico</collectingCountry>
(1831‒1840). From all those places he sent to the 
<collectionCode box="[1325,1386,1005,1031]" country="Germany" httpUri="http://grbio.org/cool/8syf-d21i" name="Museum für Naturkunde Berlin (Zoological Collections)" pageId="4" pageNumber="235" type="Museum">ZMB</collectionCode>
</materialsCitation>
<materialsCitation ID-GBIF-Occurrence="3014903331" collectionCode="ZMB" country="Haiti" pageId="4" pageNumber="235" specimenCount="1" typeStatus="holotype">
rich zoological and botanical collections (
<bibRefCitation author="Papavero, N. &amp; Ibanez-Bernal, S." box="[575,948,1040,1066]" pageId="4" pageNumber="235" pagination="65 - 173" refId="ref22788" refString="Papavero, N. &amp; Ibanez-Bernal, S. (2001) Contributions to a history of Mexican Dipterology: Part I. Entomologists and their works before the Biologia Centrali-Americana. Acta Zoologica Mexicana, 84, 65 - 173." type="journal article" year="2001">Papavero &amp; Ibáñez-Bernal 2001</bibRefCitation>
), including the specimen studied by Friese to describe this species. The 
<typeStatus box="[474,572,1076,1102]" pageId="4" pageNumber="235">holotype</typeStatus>
is currently housed at 
<collectionCode box="[829,890,1077,1103]" country="Germany" httpUri="http://grbio.org/cool/8syf-d21i" name="Museum für Naturkunde Berlin (Zoological Collections)" pageId="4" pageNumber="235" type="Museum">ZMB</collectionCode>
</materialsCitation>
